				Dolor est ipsum,  <br/> amet
				tis dolor.  Dolor est ipsum, amet tis dolor dru falak.
				</p>
				<div class="people">
					<img src="/views/images/0a3c2bcc9755c33ecdd900dc2037db4e_550.jpg">
					<img src="/views/images/guy2.jpg">
					<img src="/views/images/IMG_20130425_021516.jpg">
					<img src="/views/images/zayn-dp.jpg">
					<img src="/views/images/Maribel-Photo.jpg">
				</div>

			</span>
    </div>


</div>

